{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Finnan, a wise squirrel, loses his wife, Faemir, to tragedy and must raise his children\u00a0alone. When the Guardian of the Forest tasks him with sealing escaped monsters threatening the world, Finnan embarks on a perilous journey, wielding nature's power. While he battles monstrous foes, he meets new allies and friends as well as gain new abilities along the way.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A challenging action-platformer where players navigate diverse biomes filled with unique enemies, tough platforming challenges, and intense boss fights. Each biome introduces new abilities that expand gameplay, allowing for creative solutions to obstacles and access to hidden areas. With tight controls and punishing difficulty, the game rewards precision, mastery, and exploration. Perfect for fans of high-skill platformers and dynamic gameplay.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739544330","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398720/page.bg.jpg?t=1739544330","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398720/85889f3fc8759fd6a889f480f620283daf0852f0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739544330","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398720/85889f3fc8759fd6a889f480f620283daf0852f0/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739544330","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3501730,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Finnan, a wise squirrel, loses his wife, Faemir, to tragedy and must raise his children\u00a0alone. When the Guardian of the Forest tasks him with sealing escaped monsters threatening the world, Finnan embarks on a perilous journey, wield